<h2 class="bold font-l">Pillow Pistol - Burn Notice</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Despite laying in bed post-sex under a modesty bedsheet with no clothes on, Michael and Fiona both have guns hidden behind their pillows, which they quickly draw the moment they wake up after being disturbed. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PillowPistol" class='trope-example-link'>Pillow Pistol</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="m2gev5" data-video-descrip="Bree's orgasmic yell is loud enough for her neighbors to hear." data-video-title="A Wild Woman" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/m2gev5_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/m2gev5.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/TheImmodestOrgasm" data-video-tropename="The Immodest Orgasm" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Main/ModestyBedsheet,Creator/KyleMaclachlan,Series/DesperateHousewives,Creator/MarciaCross,Creator/DanaDelany" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/m2gev5.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">A Wild Woman</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="sk11pl" data-video-descrip="Gin is forced to sleep in the buff after her luggage with all her clothes is stolen, only for the same thief to drop in at night to talk to her." data-video-title="Nothing To Sleep With" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/sk11pl_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/snapshot_28.png" data-video-trope="Main/SleepsInTheNude" data-video-tropename="Sleeps in the Nude" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Creator/SeanConnery,Film/Entrapment,Creator/CatherineZetaJones,Main/ModestyBedsheet" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/snapshot_28.png">
<p><span class="bold">Nothing To Slee...</span></p>
