<h1 id="overlay-title">Pillow Pistol - Burn Notice</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Despite laying in bed post-sex under a modesty bedsheet with no clothes on, Michael and Fiona both have guns hidden behind their pillows, which they quickly draw the moment they wake up after being disturbed.	</p>
